#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.tshift.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.tshift"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift:1 of
msgid "Shift the time index, using the index's frequency if available."
msgstr "移动时间索引，如果可用则使用索引的频率。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift:3 of
msgid "Number of periods to move, can be positive or negative."
msgstr "要移动的周期数，可以是正数或负数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift:5 of
msgid ""
"Increment to use from the tseries module or time rule expressed as a "
"string (e.g. 'EOM')."
msgstr "使用 tseries 模块中的增量或以字符串形式表示的时间规则（例如 'EOM'）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift:8 of
msgid "Corresponds to the axis that contains the Index."
msgstr "对应包含索引的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift:11 of
msgid "**shifted**"
msgstr "**已移动**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift:15 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.tshift:16 of
msgid ""
"If freq is not specified then tries to use the freq or inferred_freq "
"attributes of the index. If neither of those attributes exist, a "
"ValueError is thrown"
msgstr ""
"如果未指定 freq，则尝试使用索引的 freq 或 inferred_freq 属性。如果这些"
"属性都不存在，则抛出 ValueError。"

